profile: Get your lawn off to the right start each year with the #1 lawn maintenance service that every lawn can benefit from -- core aeration. Unlike some lawn services that serve a single purpose, aeration supports the health of your lawn on multiple levels and is therefore the most cost-effective way to promote the health and vitality of your home's turf grass. Canadian Property Stars offers aeration as well as many other services that will make your home look its best.

profile:
Ottawa Lawn Salon is a student-owned organization that strives to deliver the highest level of customer service in the lawn maintenance and landscaping industry. We do this by keeping our client-employee ratio low and in-turn fostering close relationships with our community which often last for years to come. 

All this is done while providing employment for students - we take our of our team as our family and in turn, they take care of our clients like it's their business. The result: You get the efficiency, quality, and reliability of a big company with the attention to detail of a small owner-operated company. 

Contact us today and let us show you how we can impress you!

profile:
Finally, the lawn experts are here! We are your trusted lawn maintenance specialist, and we want to make your lawn flush and green! Through our hard work, proven system and scientifically backed methods we bring something which has been missing in all but the wealthiest lawn care projects- a personalized lawn care experience. Gone are the days of absent mindedly throwing more fertilizer, more seed and spraying the weeds down to no avail. If it didn’t work the first time, it certainly won’t the second or third time. By making use of the latest horticultural research, we optimize your soil to provide the ideal growing conditions for your lawn. We specialize in sod installation, and make sure that it actually survives! With us, we get the job done right the first time!

Visit us at https://www.thesodboys.ca/ for more information!
